                    <span>I bought this book about 5 years ago for work to teach myself how to write VxD's and it was invaluable. Windows Me is the last OS that book pertains to, but if you need to learn how to write VxD's this is the book.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Great for starters</div>
